Use scons to compile both the tigre library and the earth sample:

Tigre library
=============

Compile: scons -f tigre.py -f app.py 
Clean: scons -f tigre.py -f app.py -c

GLFW
====

Compile: scons -f glfw.py
Clean: scons -f glfw.py -c

Qt
==

Compile: qmake && make
Clean: make clean (objects), make distclean (everything else)
